author: By REBECCA BOONE Associated Press
title: Hundreds defy Idaho's stay-at-home order at Capitol protest
description: BOISE, Idaho (AP) — More than 1,000 protesters gathered at the Idaho Statehouse Friday afternoon in defiance of Gov. Brad Little’s extension of the statewide stay-at-home order.
content:
BOISE, Idaho (AP) More than 1,000 protesters gathered at the Idaho Statehouse Friday afternoon in defiance of Gov. Brad Littles extension of the statewide stay-at-home order.
